&lt;h2 id="solutions">Solutions &lt;a href="#solutions" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="chat-with-a-single-user">Chat with a single user &lt;a href="#chat-with-a-single-user" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true">&lt;i class="material-icons align-middle">link&lt;/i>&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;p>Use the write command:&lt;/p>



 
 
 

 
 
 
 

 

 &lt;div class="prism-codeblock ">
 &lt;pre id="7e38cb3" class="language-bash ">
 &lt;code>write user_you_want_to_talk_to&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;p>Then type your message and press Enter to validate.&lt;/p>
